{"tid":1855179,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(新中国肺炎之戰) 傳取消東京奧運　日本急澄清","createTime":"2020-02-01T03:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T03:05:46.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"450217041822f6f93ad319519f62f09a97b27106","tid":1855179,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:01:27.000Z","msg":"世界衞生組織緊急顧問委員會周四（30日）正式宣布，將由新冠狀病毒引起的武漢肺炎，列為國際公共衞生緊急事件後，網上立刻盛傳今年8月的東京奧運及殘奧將會取消。對此，日本五輪（奧運）相橋本聖子昨日在記者會上再三否認，強調只屬謠言，並重申會做足準備，與有關機構加強合作，保證大會安全。<br />\n<br />\n據知，國際奧委會與世界衞生組織確曾展開會談，惟僅是集中在「控制傳染病」方面，並未討論取消或推遲東京奧運。事實由1896年首屆奧運至今，只得1916年柏林、1940年東京及1944年倫敦三屆，因第1及第2次世界大戰取消，從未試過因為戰爭以外因素未能舉行。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20200201/bkn-20200201000555202-0201_00882_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"265f790d451994839a7ff20d17fbafb584624148","tid":1855179,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:04:09.000Z","msg":"取消中國隊資格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738c6dee99b3848092734c3984af51f1b5cccfaa","tid":1855179,"uid":224882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"265f790d451994839a7ff20d17fbafb584624148","tid":1855179,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:04:09.000Z","msg":"取消中國隊資格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:04:49.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1f866ad23f61ae197bf75e1a4689f2cd2544b4","tid":1855179,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:05:46.000Z","msg":"唔俾佢地入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}